# Backend (FastAPI)

- Routers thin; business logic in `services/`; contracts in `schemas/`.
- GET/read endpoints must not mutate state (no recovery/normalization on page load).
- Admin endpoints explicit; 401/403/404/422; no raw stack traces to public clients.
- Preserve `request_id`, warnings, debug fields in responses.
- Async where already used; mirror existing layering.

## Sensitive domains

Publication, visibility, route eligibility, import jobs, review queue, debug reports — read code + tests before changing.

## Commands

`.venv/bin/python -m pytest tests/<target> -q --no-cov`
